{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2f372d8bed","title":"给龙伯坚的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"95d6a350ca","index":0,"year":1950,"month":3,"day":14,"articleId":"2f372d8bed"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"1d6b070286","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"龙伯坚，原名龙莹，五四运动时曾主编期刊《新湖南》。当时任湖南省临时政府卫生处处长。"},{"id":"d4582e3724","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指新中国成立初期中共湖南省委创办的《新湖南报》与五四时期龙莹、毛泽东先后主编过的期刊《新湖南》名称相同。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7165184447","type":"title","text":"给龙伯坚“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed"},{"id":"1d6b070286","type":"paragraph","text":"伯坚先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed"},{"id":"d4582e3724","type":"paragraph","text":"去年十一月十一日大示收到读悉。吾兄参加革命，从事卫生工作，极为欣感。新湖南报名是湖南同志们起的，与从前报名偶合以，引起你的高兴，我亦与有荣幸。旧词无足取，不必重写。尚望努力工作，为民服务。顺颂大安！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed"},{"id":"e73e0e2da6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed"},{"id":"bd138f62b6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年三月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed"}],"page":{"id":"f667e7b36e","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"2f372d8bed","start":236,"end":236}}}},"__N_SSG":true}